  <text>
    <body>
      <head>TEI DSE-AS: A TEI Customization for the Digital Scholarly Edition Annemarie Schwarzenbach</head>

      <p>This document defines TEI DSE-AS, a customization of the <ref target="https://tei-c.org/guidelines/">TEI
        Guidelines</ref> designed for the <ref target="https://annemarie-schwarzenbach.ch/">Digital Scholarly Edition
        Annemarie Schwarzenbach</ref> (DSE-AS).</p>

      <p>The customization selects elements from eleven TEI modules and constrains their usage to match the project's
        editorial conventions. It covers the encoding of:
        <list>
          <item>Letters and short forms with their specific structural components (opener, closer, postscript, dateline,
            salute, figures with captions, floating text blocks, etc.)</item>
          <item>Correspondence metadata via <gi>correspDesc</gi> and <gi>correspAction</gi></item>
          <item>Editorial interventions: corrections (<gi>choice</gi>/<gi>sic</gi>/<gi>corr</gi>), expansions of
            abbreviations (<gi>choice</gi>/<gi>abbr</gi>/<gi>expan</gi>), additions (<gi>add</gi>), deletions
            (<gi>del</gi>), gaps (<gi>gap</gi>), and unclear readings (<gi>unclear</gi>)</item>
          <item>Manuscript description via <gi>msDesc</gi> for archival source information</item>
          <item>Facsimile linking via <gi>facsimile</gi>, <gi>surface</gi>, and <gi>zone</gi></item>
          <item>Index entries using <gi>rs</gi> with typed references to persons, places, organizations, bibliographical
            entries, correspondences, images, letters, short forms, long forms, and travels</item>
          <item>Rendition features following DTA conventions (bold, italic, underline, superscript, subscript, letter
            spacing)</item>
          <item>Gemination marks (<gi>g</gi>) for historical handwriting conventions</item>
          <item>Lists of events (<gi>listEvent</gi>) and keyword classifications (<gi>keywords</gi>)</item>
        </list>
      </p>

      <p>For the full edition model and transcription criteria, see the <ref
        target="https://docs.annemarie-schwarzenbach.ch/editionsmodell">DSE-AS documentation</ref>. The source code of
        this customization is maintained at <ref target="https://github.com/dse-as/oxygen-framework"
        >github.com/dse-as/oxygen-framework</ref>.</p>
      <schemaSpec ident="tei_dseas" start="TEI listEvent list" prefix="tei_" targetLang="en" docLang="en">
        
        <!-- header module: metadata, correspondence description, profiles, and language declarations -->
        <moduleRef key="header" include="teiHeader fileDesc titleStmt publicationStmt sourceDesc correspDesc textClass notesStmt keywords profileDesc catRef correspAction idno edition editionStmt language langUsage"/>
        
        <!-- core module: paragraphs, references, editorial interventions, page/line breaks, etc. -->
        <moduleRef key="core" include="p title rs note head pb lb lg l address addrLine cb listBibl bibl add del abbr quote unclear gap hi list item date publisher graphic author foreign editor ref milestone choice expan sic corr biblScope respStmt label ptr"/>
        
        <!-- textstructure module: document structure, letter components, floating text -->
        <moduleRef key="textstructure" include="TEI text body opener closer front back div salute dateline signed postscript byline floatingText"/>
        
        <!-- tei module: infrastructure classes used by other modules -->
        <moduleRef key="tei"/>
        
        <!-- elements selected from different modules -->
        <moduleRef key="msdescription" include="msDesc msIdentifier repository altIdentifier additional surrogates collection"/>
        <moduleRef key="gaiji" include="g"/>
        <moduleRef key="namesdates" include="orgName persName placeName listEvent event"/>
        <moduleRef key="transcr" include="facsimile surface zone fw space handShift"/>
        <moduleRef key="linking" include="ab anchor seg"/>
        <moduleRef key="figures" include="table row cell figure"/>
        <moduleRef key="analysis" include="pc"/>
        
        <!-- add attribute classes needed from other modules -->
        <classRef key="att.global.analytic"/>

        <!-- delete unused attribute classes -->
        <classSpec type="atts" ident="att.cmc" mode="delete"/>
        <classSpec type="atts" ident="att.global.change" mode="delete"/>
        <classSpec type="atts" ident="att.global.source" mode="delete"/>
        <classSpec type="atts" ident="att.ranging" mode="delete"/>
        
        <!-- delete some attributes from global linking -->
        <classSpec type="atts" ident="att.global.linking" mode="change">
          <attList>
            <attDef ident="synch" mode="delete"/>
            <attDef ident="copyOf" mode="delete"/>
            <attDef ident="next" mode="delete"/>
            <attDef ident="prev" mode="delete"/>
            <attDef ident="exclude" mode="delete"/>
            <attDef ident="select" mode="delete"/>
          </attList>
        </classSpec>
        
        <!-- delete some attributes from global rendition -->
        <classSpec type="atts" ident="att.global.rendition" mode="change">
          <attList>
            <attDef ident="rend" mode="delete"/>
            <attDef ident="style" mode="delete"/>
          </attList>
        </classSpec>

        <!-- delete @cert from global responsibility -->
        <classSpec type="atts" ident="att.global.responsibility" mode="change">
          <attList>
            <attDef ident="cert" mode="delete"/>
          </attList>
        </classSpec>
        
        <!-- change existing elements -->

        <elementSpec ident="add" module="core" mode="change">
          <attList>
            <attDef ident="place" mode="change" usage="req">
              <valList type="closed" mode="replace">
                <valItem ident="top"><desc>at the top of the page</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="bottom"><desc>at the foot of the page</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="above"><desc>above the line</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="right"><desc>to the right</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="below"><desc>below the line</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="left"><desc>to the left</desc></valItem>
              </valList>
            </attDef>
          </attList>
        </elementSpec>
        
        <elementSpec ident="g" module="core" mode="change">
          <attList>
            <attDef ident="ref" mode="change" usage="req">
              <valList type="closed" mode="replace">
                <valItem ident="#ngem"><desc>ngem</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="#mngem"><desc>mngem</desc></valItem>
              </valList>
            </attDef>
          </attList>
        </elementSpec>
        
        <elementSpec ident="gap" module="core" mode="change">
          <attList>
            <attDef ident="reason" mode="change" usage="req">
              <valList type="closed" mode="replace">
                <valItem ident="illegible"><desc>illegible</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="lost"><desc>lost</desc></valItem>
              </valList>
            </attDef>
            <attDef ident="hand" mode="delete"/>
          </attList>
        </elementSpec>
        
        <elementSpec ident="hi" module="core" mode="change">
          <attList>
            <attDef ident="rendition" mode="change" usage="opt">
              <valList type="closed" mode="replace">
                <valItem ident="#b"><desc>bold</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="#i"><desc>italics</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="#u"><desc>underline</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="#sub"><desc>subscript</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="#sup"><desc>superscript</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="#g"><desc>spaced (gesperrt)</desc></valItem>
              </valList>
            </attDef>
          </attList>
        </elementSpec>
        
        <elementSpec ident="rs" module="core" mode="change">
          <attList>
            <attDef ident="type" mode="change" usage="req">
              <valList type="closed" mode="replace">
                <valItem ident="bibl"><desc>Bibliographical entry</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="correspondence"><desc>Correspondence</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="image"><desc>Image</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="letter"><desc>Letter</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="longform"><desc>Longform</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="org"><desc>Organisation</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="person"><desc>Person</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="place"><desc>Place</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="smallform"><desc>Smallform</desc></valItem>
                <valItem ident="travel"><desc>Travel</desc></valItem>
              </valList>
            </attDef>
          </attList>
        </elementSpec>
        
      </schemaSpec>
    </body>
  </text>
</TEI>